{
  "_note": "Inferred response field overlay for routes WITHOUT a captured body. Applied by scripts/harvest-response-fields.mjs ONLY to routes that have no `verified` fields, marked fieldsSource:'inferred'. Each entry: match (substring of the route url, optionally method-scoped) -> the response keys an agent reads. These are from documented RH conventions + this repo's SKILL/AGENTS, NOT live-verified for the exact route; re-running the harvester against a real capture upgrades them to verified. Keys only, never values.",
